Summary: A Week of UFO Sightings in Irvington
divs: Sighting DetailsI did not witness these UFOS personally, but dozens in the surrounding area have been claiming they are seeing UFOs at night over Irvington, AL and the surrounding areas. It was picked up and sensationalized this morning by at least one radio station (97.5 WABD). The radio station also has photographs of the objects from last night and earlier this week. I'm uploading one of the photographs but there are apparently others.
